{"tid":1474622,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"揮動染血的美國國旗，勝利可能會出現","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T13:05:16.000Z","uid":267970,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"375b83588ef093c54dbeded8ecea21aa14e536e1","tid":1474622,"uid":267970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n請你盡量別受傷<br />\n<br />\n但如果你真係受傷，請緊抱美國國旗，把你的血流在旗幟身上然後大力揮動，讓國際看看，我們為自由付出的不是看，是血。<br />\n<br />\n國際記者們，其實正在等，等一個血淚，悲哀而正義的報導。這個報導一出，就是香港人的勝利。<br />\n<br />\n所以，當你在記者面前，受了傷仍大力揮動染上血的美國國旗，勝利大概就會出現。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"30aff96a4e1c20f5e6809e4ab5eaca987b74f521","tid":1474622,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_